(Dark Mouse, it's a role playing through e-mail, sort of like in writing. 
Some people are more descriptive than others. There are three groups now: 
The Maximals, The Predacons, and The Alliance. But now the Predacons had 
split up on two groups. Megatron's group and Hell Beast's group. Here, 
something like this.)


Quickstrike:







Quickstrike studied Hiss cautiously. He wasn't going to run into anything 
like it was a brick wall. They could turn him into Hell Beast. He wasn't 
going to do that. Hell Beast would kill him.

"Tell me who, or ah's ain't goin'." he said. "What was he like? What he 
sound like?" He wasn't to take chances. But it could be the clone of 
Tarantsulus.

It made his head turn, but he was relieved that he was no longer 
light-headed with the poision. He looked over to Shredder, and said lowly to 
him, "Get the others here. And don't argue." He still wanted to lead.
